-----------------------------------------------------------------------
1.1.8   2013-08-31
    * Indent style has been updated: 8 width tab => 4 space characters.

1.1.7   2012-08-14
    * Add ``chmod a+x'' in Makefile.

1.1.6   2010-06-02
    * Remove 2 options: -e and -j completely.
    * Update help message.
    * Add README.JA

1.1.5   2010-05-31
    * Initialize the pointer: **selected_language = NULL;
    * Add language file: jp.h and en.h
    * Remove unused variable.
    * Remove 2 options: -e and -j. Use -Lx option.
    * Default language is English.

1.1.4   2009-08-09
    * Add the new option '-L', select displaying language(e or j)
    * Japanese characters are written by UTF-8.

1.1.3   2009-04-29
    * New macro 'DEFAULT_LANGUAGE'
    * New compile time macro 'DAIJI'

1.1.2   2009-02-11
    * Correct spell('Hyphen') in English mode.
    * Add the new option '-dh': Use '-' as a delimiter.

1.1.1   2008-10-18
    * fprintf() typecasts to the void.

1.1.0   2008-04-01
    * Commit in Hokkaido !
    * Remove the option -x(debug mode).

1.0.15  2008-02-17
    * Add description of '-C' option in the help screen.
    * The number 32(dec) is replaced by the character ' '(Space).

1.0.14  2008-02-11
    * Add the new option '-C': shows control character.
    * Fix for the case that includes multibyte character.

1.0.13  2008-01-27
    * Fix usage of the following functions, strlen(), strlcpy() .

1.0.12  2008-01-26
    * Use the following string functions: isprint(), iscntrl(), and
      tolower().

1.0.11  2007-12-30
    * Check the length of the string while read from stdin.

1.0.10  2007-12-29
    * c2p recieves string from STDIN.

1.0.9   2006-09-15
    * Add the new compile macro 'KANJI'.  Some symbols and numbers
      are output as KANJI.
    * Add another pronunciations in comment.

1.0.8   2006-06-02
    * Uses EXIT_SUCCESS or EXIT_FAILURE (stdlib.h) at exit status.

1.0.7   2004-05-05
    * Support white spaces in the argument.

1.0.6   2004-04-29
    * Fix: Skip if control character was appeared.
    * Fix: Skip if multibyte character was appeared.
    * Fix: Exit if invalid option was specified.

1.0.5   2003-01-07
    * Add the New option '-s' to write a white space after a delim-
      iter.
    * Add pre-processor for the system that has no 'strlcpy'

1.0.4   2002-12-30
    * Add the new delimiter ' ': White space.

1.0.3   2002-12-23
    * Fixed declaration of some variables to compile with gcc 2.96.

1.0.2   1997-10-01
    * Add the new option -d: Delimiter.

1.0.1   1997-08-31
    * Add the new function help() and the new option '-h'.
    * Add the new option -v: to print the version number.

1.0.0   1997-04-29
    * Initial version: c2p is a converter which  convert from char-
      acter(string) to phonetic code.
